longBusinessSummary: Qlucore AB (publ) provides visualization-based bioinformatics data analysis tools for research and precision diagnostics in Sweden and internationally. Its products include Qlucore Omics Explorer, a bioinformatics software for research in life science, biotech, and plant industries, as well as academia; Qlucore Insights, a software for clinical data analysis; and Qlucore Diagnostics, a software platform for multi-omics companion. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Lund, Sweden.
